      "raw": "Education\nMasters in Teaching English as an Additional Languages (TEAL)\n, Simon Fraser University, BC,Canada.(2019)\nTESOL Diploma\n, ILAC College, Vancouver, BC, Canada.\nMasters in English Language Teaching ( ELT)\nfrom East West University, Bangladesh\nBA in English (ELT)\n, East West University, Bangladesh"
